# Phase 6: Security & Compliance (Vertex AI & IAM)

This phase focuses on hardening the Antigravity ecosystem by centralizing secret management, implementing comprehensive auditing of all external AI calls, and enforcing rate limits to prevent cost overruns.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Security & Vault
We will introduce a centralized `KeyVault` to replace scattered `os.getenv` calls and provide a foundation for future IAM/Context-aware security.

#### [NEW] [key_vault.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/src/antigravity_core/key_vault.py)
A central utility to:
- Load secrets from [.env](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/.env) or structured configuration.
- Categorize keys by service (Gemini, Mistral, Kaggle, Vertex).
- Provide unified access with optional "Context" checks.

#### [MODIFY] [gemini_client.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/src/antigravity_core/gemini_client.py)
- Refactor [__init__](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/harvester.py#17-26) to use `KeyVault.get_gemini_keys()`.

#### [MODIFY] [mistral_client.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/src/antigravity_core/mistral_client.py)
- Refactor [__init__](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/harvester.py#17-26) to use `KeyVault.get_mistral_key()`.

