### [Component] Observability & Audit
We will implement detailed tracking for every external API interaction.

#### [NEW] [audit_logger.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/audit_logger.py)
A specialized logger that writes to `audit_logs.jsonl`:
- Record: `timestamp`, `service`, `payload_size`, `session_id`, `outcome`.
- Integrated with [JudgeGuard](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/judge_guard.py#82-427) for real-time compliance monitoring.

#### [MODIFY] [judge_guard.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/judge_guard.py)
- Update `audit_log` method to use the new `AuditLogger`.
- Implement rate-limiting logic: block calls if daily usage exceeds [trinity_config.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/trinity_config.json) thresholds.

