## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `pytest tests/test_security.py`: Verify that `KeyVault` returns correct keys and respects context.
- `python3 scripts/audit_logger.py --test`: Verify that entries are correctly written to `audit_logs.jsonl`.
- Simulate rate-limit breach: Temporarily set threshold to 0 in [trinity_config.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/trinity_config.json) and verify that [JudgeGuard](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/judge_guard.py#82-427) blocks the call.

